title: ‘The Ultimatum’ Episodes 5-8 Breakdown, Plus an Interview With Jake and Randall!
description:
Amelia Wedemeyer is joined by Callie Curry to chat about episodes 5-8 of Netflix’s newest hit, 'The Ultimatum: Marry or Move On' (1:00). Then, Amelia sits down with 'Ultimatum' cast members Randall Griffin and Jake Cunningham, who give us some major behind-the-scenes tea that we did NOT see coming (40:15).
Hosts: Amelia Wedemeyer and Callie Curry
Producers: Devon Manze and Chelsea Stark-Jones
